title: scav - Scavenger Hunt April 2006
name: scav - Scavenger Hunt April 2006
description:
A Map by Tanabutler

My goal is to use as many of my own photographs as I can, since I am a traveling photographer. With 19 exceptions, these are all my own photographs. I did not get the plastic horse tied to a curb, nor an outdoor power outlet. Everything else on the list is here!

: D
